cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or reference this work, please cite it as below."
type: software

title: "AIIP — Asistente Inteligente de Inmunodeficiencias Primarias"
abstract: >
  Conversational agent based on RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) designed
  to support families and medical professionals facing questions related to
  Primary Immunodeficiencies (PID). Built with a Zero False Negative safety
  architecture, the system never confirms a situation as safe and always
  directs users toward medical consultation. Developed as a Master's thesis
  in Artificial Intelligence in collaboration with a pediatric immunologist.

